        "description": "Nucleus Dynamic Warfare — a combined-arms sandbox for the Nucleus platform. You fly a Boscali trainer over your fleet (Fleet Carrier + Destroyer + Frigate + Corvette) with two friendly fighters airborne; Primeva forces (a northern surface group + airborne fighters/bomber/CAS) are spread across the map. Open the map and use the bezel buttons: CMD (place orders + set commander mode OFF/MANUAL/ASSISTED/AUTO), BLD (buy convoys), SQD (manage squads), WAR (campaign view: operations + battle feed). Set AUTO and watch the theater commander run the war, or take a slice manually. The persistent two-faction campaign (Warfare) saves and resumes across sessions.",
